      <span class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/70 font-mono tracking-wider">@gitlab</span>
      <span class="mt-4 text-xs text-white/40 font-mono text-center max-w-xs">Open source projects, experiments, and more on my GitLab profile.</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-full md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 md:col-start-1 md:row-start-5 bg-[#18191A] border-[#E49245]/20 border-2 rounded-xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
